{
  "stem": "25114.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we came to the pushcha, I-- I-- a doctor came in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was getting a bit-- I think-- I think a bit bigger.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went to this doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was a gynecologist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she examined me, and she said, you are fifth month pregnant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She said, I can't perform an abortion-- because there were quite a few women, pregnant, that performed abortions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can't perform abortion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You've got to wait till you're six months pregnant, and we can make, uh-- I think, a-- a premature [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] birth, sort of like.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Child who were born but not live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Which a lot of people did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're going through the same pains and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of people did this, because this-- in spite of everything, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, people were people, and life was short, and people were coupling up together, you know, men and women.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They feel safer together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And normal life took place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So anyway, she said to me, well, we have to wait another month or one and a half months.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When the time comes, we'll perform this abortion on you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then came the big hunt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Shortly afterwards came-- came the big hunt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was probably started in August, or something-- or in July.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After we came to-- to the pushcha.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The big hunt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went through-- this was the most terrible thing that could happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we were besieged.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Real-- three divisions, I think, they had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A big [INAUDIBLE], because the-- there was-- '43, they were already losing in Stalingrad, and they were already losing the war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the partisans made such a damage to the German army.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
